DOC_LEVEL: L1
MODULE: pipeline
PATH: dev-pipeline/**
DESCRIPTION: automation scripts + templates for feature/bugfix pipelines

KEY_FILES:
- dev-pipeline/run.sh
- dev-pipeline/run-bugfix.sh
- dev-pipeline/launch-daemon.sh
- dev-pipeline/launch-bugfix-daemon.sh
- dev-pipeline/retry-feature.sh
- dev-pipeline/retry-bug.sh
- dev-pipeline/reset-feature.sh
- dev-pipeline/scripts/path_policy.py
- dev-pipeline/scripts/*.py
- dev-pipeline/templates/*

STATE_PATHS:
- dev-pipeline/state/
- dev-pipeline/bugfix-state/

DAEMON_LOG_POLICY:
- feature daemon log -> dev-pipeline/state/pipeline-daemon.log
- bugfix daemon log -> dev-pipeline/bugfix-state/pipeline-daemon.log

TRAPS:
- several large operational scripts (>500 lines) require cautious edits
- TODO density is concentrated in this module

SUBDIRS:
- dev-pipeline/scripts -> .prizm-docs/pipeline/scripts.prizm

DECISIONS:
- 2026-03-09 | pipeline-doc-init | treat shell+python pipeline as independent module
- 2026-03-10 | f001-path-policy-shared | centralize feature/bug/session/session-status/daemon-log paths via scripts/path_policy.py and JS mirror module
- 2026-03-10 | f001-us3-scope | include logs/reset in runner+service API surface using daemon wrappers and clean reset commands
